Chop artichoke hearts. Set aside. In medium bowl stir together cream cheese and mayonnaise. Stir in artichoke hearts, Parmesan cheese and onions. Fold in imitation crabmeat. Spoon into 9-inch pie plate or two 2-cup casseroles**. Bake, uncovered, at 375 degrees F about 25 minutes or until heated through. Garnish as desired. Serve with crackers.